T02TD3626E:245a-1: ba ra ma aa shva s'a dha nam /
T02TD3626E:245a-5: de bzhin du nyi ma la h'um yig mthing ga las skyes pa'i rta mchog dmar po zhal bzhi pa /
T02TD3626E:245a-8: zhal dang po khro zhing sgeg pa /
T02TD3626E:245a-12: steng zhal mchu rol zhing rta'i zhal ljang gu /
T02TD3626E:245b-0: phyag g-yas kyi gcig gis sna @245b tshogs rdo rje dang bcas shing bzhengs pa'i tshul du byas pa /
T02TD3626E:245b-1: phyag g-yon gyi gcig gis ral gri dang bcas pa'i sna tshogs padma bsnams pa'o //
T02TD3626E:245b-2: slar yang g-yas kyi ba dan gsum phyag gis blang ba'i tshul mdzad pa /
T02TD3626E:245b-3: slar yang phyag g-yon gyis mdung bsnams pa /
T02TD3626E:245b-4: slar yang g-yas kyi phyag gis ral gri dang /
T02TD3626E:245b-6: g-yon gyi phyag lhag mas dbyug pa dang /
T02TD3626E:245b-9: g-yas kyi gcig gis dbang mo dang /
T02TD3626E:245b-11: g-yas kyi zhabs gnyis pas 'dod lha dang /
T02TD3626E:245b-13: g-yon pa'i zhabs gcig gis dbang mo dang /
T02TD3626E:245b-14: sbrang rtsir byed pa mnan pa /
T02TD3626E:245b-15: g-yon gyi zhabs gnyis pas rgyal bar byed pa dang /
T02TD3626E:245b-17: bdag nyid de lta bur bsgom par bya'o //
T02TD3626E:245b-18: sna tshogs rdo rje dang ba dan gsum pa bsgreng ba ni /
T02TD3626E:245b-21: aom sumbha ni sumbha h'um zhes so //
T02TD3626E:245b-22: rta mchog gi sgrub thabs rdzogs so//
